 you. If someone cares about you\, then you should feel comfortable telling
  them that all youve been thinking about ever since you met them is if Mus
 ic Trivia with Brendan and Sean is ever going to come back to Space. Well\
 , it is. If you cant tell\, they let us write the blurb about our little m
 usic questions thing. Its going pretty great so far. Spring will have spru
 ng by the time this rolls around. Youll be feeling good again. That makes 
 us happy. Come hang out in Spaces beautiful lobby\, and grimace and grin t
 hrough 6 rounds of what might be our best questions yet. RSVP so we know y
 oure actually coming\, and actually show up if you RSVP. If you can. Doors
  open at 2:30pm and the questions start flowing around 3pm. Its free\, and
  you could even win prizes like free tickets or merch. Okay\, great blurb.
