 ortalimages/portalimages/8GVvHqDMbEewojpTxLlrXA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:A Legacy in Miniature: Rotary’s Fight to End Polio\n\nTo hon
 or Rotary’s decades-long commitment to eradicating polio\, miniature art
 ists from around the world were invited to recreate powerful moments from 
 this historic global effort. The pieces are currently on display at One Ro
 tary Center\, and the public is invited to view the art and learn more abo
 ut the fight to end polio worldwide.
LOCATION:One Rotary Center
URL:https://magazine.rotary.org/rotary/october_2025/MobilePagedArticle.act
 ion?articleId=2085663#articleId2085663
