 ortalimages/portalimages/v9oLPn8qB0ObkaS-UW5rdA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Caregiver's Circle is an in-person conversation for anyone
  in a caregiving role to elders\, partners\, and young people\, co-facilit
 ated by a National Board Certified Health and Wellness Coach and a license
 d mental health professional. We will focus on sharing experiences\, resou
 rces\, and help participants leave with strategies about caring for themse
 lves while caring for others.
LOCATION:Zora's Place
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
