DESCRIPTION:Chicago Danztheatre Ensemble \\(CDE\\) is pleased to present P
 oetry In Beat\, April 11 at 7:30 p.m.\, at Chicago Danztheatre\, 1650 W. F
 oster Ave.\n\nPoetry In Beat features poetry\, live music and tap dance un
 iting to challenge the stifled emotions born under the weight of our curre
 nt administration. This performance allows cacophony to become the cathars
 is with a rhythmic uprising of sound and soul\, guiding the audience back 
 to the connection\, community and collective strength in uncertain times.\
 n\nTickets for Poetry In Beat are on sale for $10 - $20. To purchase ticke
 ts\, visit DanzTheatre.org.
