 a in F Major GEMINIANI - Concerto\, ?La Follia? CORELLI - Concerto Grosso\
 , op. 6\, no. 11 NARDINI - Concerto for Violin\, op. 1\, no. 1 VIVALDI - C
 oncerto for 2 Violins in G Minor PUGNANI - Sinfonia in B - flat Major Ital
 ian violinist and conductor Fabio Biondi\, world - renowned for ?blazing\,
