 Europa Galante\, leads a high - voltage program centered around Vivaldi\, 
 those who inspired him \\(Geminiani and Corelli\\)\, and those he inspired
 \, like Nardini and Pugnani. Concertmaster Gina DiBello joins Biondi for V
 ivaldi?s Concerto for 2 Violins in G Minor. Make new discoveries and hear 
 familiar favorites afresh! Music of the Baroque Orchestra Fabio Biondi\, c
 onductor& violin Gina DiBello\, violin
