BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Centennial Needlepoint Reception
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260412T160000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260412T180000
UID:260327QiE8lm3dY0iC16MicAnZ4g
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/IOmAZCgKXEiNd9K0KW6jwQ.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:To mark the village’s centennial in 1996\, a group of reside
 nts created a remarkable needlepoint depicting many of the community’s m
 ost important sites\, including numerous historic homes. This beautiful pi
 ece is displayed in the boardroom of the Stuart Memorial Building\, though
  its story may not be widely known.\n\nJoin us as we showcase the needlepo
 int\, explore its history\, and identify the featured sites. Two of the or
 iginal needle pointers will share insights into the process and this labor
  of love. Ellen Castellini will also speak briefly about the resurgence of
  needlepoint and her passion for the art form.\n\nThe reception will inclu
 de complimentary appetizers and beverages.\n\nPlease register in advance a
 t https://kenilworthhistory.org/needlepoint-reception/
LOCATION:Kenilworth Historical Society
URL:https://kenilworthhistory.org/needlepoint-reception/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
