DESCRIPTION:On April 15th IYRT is hosting a free BYO-picnic at communal ta
 ble along the Lakefill.\n\nJoin us at a long communal table down the lengt
 h of Northwestern's Lakefill and enjoy a spring evening picnic dinner with
  friends. This free event is a chance for us to come together\, share a me
 al\, talk\, and have fun. If You're Reading This provides tables and chair
 s\; participants bring friends\, food\, and utensils.\n\nYou can organize 
 a group and nominate a table captain \\(the person whose name we will writ
 e on your designated table\\)\, or come by yourself and we'll seat you wit
 h others--all are welcome!\n\nIf you would like to volunteer as a table ca
 ptain\, be a greeter\, help with setup and breakdown\, or photograph/do vi
 deo\, please email us at: ifyourereadingthisnu@gmail.com\n\nFor more infor
 mation on other Longest Table events\, go to longesttablecommunity.org\n\
 nSee you at Northwestern's Longest Table!
LOCATION:Northwestern Lakefill
