DESCRIPTION:In the 25 years since the release of her debut record\, Hometo
 wn\, tail-gunning blues virtuoso Ana Popovic has proved herself a force of
  nature with a vintage Stratin hand. Guitar WorldAna Popovic Melds Rock\, 
 Blues\, and Jazz for Fiery Power No DepressionA badass with a silver Strat
 \, she performs the heck out of this song \\[Worked Up\\]\, owning it with
  swagger and grace. Worked Up captures her love of funky grooves plus the 
 edginess of rocking guitar power. Rock & Blues Muse Los Angeles-based and 
 critically acclaimed guitarist and singerAna Popovic is set to release her
  highly anticipated album Dance To The Rhythm \\(Electric Heel Records\\) 
 on September 26\, 2025. Produced by Popovic and Buthel\, the album showcas
 es a groundbreaking fusion of groove\, blues\, funk\, and soul.
