UID:260325np0LLVaz7U6Yr85Oqwow4Q
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/1rrYxTFvREGIaKXfh54zmA.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:About This Event\n\nJoin us for a special event featuring The
  Bad Momz of Comedy! Enjoy an evening of stand-up comedy as a small showc
 ase of hilarious comics share relatable stories about the humorous side of
  parenting and everyday family life. Gather your friends and fellow parent
 s for an entertaining and lighthearted night out. We hope you’ll join u
 s for great laughs and a wonderful opportunity to connect with our Baker D
 emonstration School community!\n\nEvent Date and Time: Thursday\, April 23
 \, 2026 \n\n6:00 pm - Doors open for guests\n\n7:00 pm - Performance star
 ts \n\nLocation: 201 Sheridan Rd\, Wilmette\, IL 60091  \n\n\\(free par
 king available in lot\, entrance on Maple Ave\\)\n\n$45 ticket price inclu
 des snacks and one drink\n\n\\(purchase 4 or more tickets at $40\\)\n\nAbo
 ut Bad Momz of Comedy: \n\nBad Momz of Comedy\, as seen on the Kelly Clark
 son Show\, continues to sell out shows across the country -- making moms a
 nd men laugh. Founded by Chicago-based comic Orly KG in 2022\, each Bad Mo
 mz of Comedy show utilizes a small showcase of hilarious comics from its g
 rowing roster of 80\\+ influential mom/female comics. Previously packed ve
 nues include Zanies Nashville\, Chicago\, and Rosemont\, Illinois as well 
 as St. Louis City Winery\, Chicago's Theater on the Lake\, and more. @badm
 omzofcomedy on all socials.\n\nBad Momz Reel:\n\nwww.facebook.com/OrlyKGCo
 medy/videos/1035733347421812
