BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SPINOFF
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260423T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260423T210000
UID:260318SKxpqcc4tU-OUaK2pXYX1g
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/IkS4GEmr9kqB0RBq4JAebg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Two years ago\, Alé left the city to move back into their chi
 ldhood home to caretake for their mother. Far from friends\, their plans i
 n the wind\, Alé turned to the familiar world of TV sitcoms for comfort. 
 That’s when Alé discovered Frasier.\n\nNow\, it’s time for Alé ’s
  SPINOFF. Using the script of Frasier as a roadmap\, the cast of performer
 s will explore this time in Alé’s life\, deconstructing the sitcom form
  through the Neo-Futurist lens. Who are we to our parents\, who are they t
 o us\, what’s changed in the years apart?\n\nThe parent and the child. T
 he character and the person. Living under the same roof again\, will they 
 get picked up for syndication? Or canceled before they can tell the whole 
 story?
LOCATION:The Neo-Futurist Theater
URL:https://www.choosechicago.com/event/spinoff/2026-04-23/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
