DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260429T193000
UID:260221w4A2xwmm1EGlfd7yZoTpEQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/6cOGB4zZXkeVNuvUQVAAAg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:The Flat Five is a Chicago-based pop vocal supergroup Kelly Ho
 gan\, Nora OConnor\, Scott Ligon\, Casey McDonough\, Alex Hall made of fiv
 e in-demand musicians who individually spend much of their time touring an
 d recording with bands like Neko Case\, NRBQ\, The Decemberists\, Andrew B
 ird\, Mavis Staples\, Iron and Wine\, Jakob Dylan\, Robbie Fulks\, Alejand
 ro Escovedo\, The New Pornographers\, J.D. McPherson and many other heavy 
 hitters. These five folks stay very\, very busy. Yet for the past 10 years
 \, these shameless harmony junkies came together\, like a moth to a porchl
 ight\, to make music as The Flat Five. Purely for the love of singing toge
 ther. For the mother-effing fun of it.
LOCATION:Evanston SPACE
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/the-flat-five/18170694/2026-04-29T19
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
