UID:260301mUti_gW9oUKfZ2CRejdCmQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/-FzPe1CFoE-1ufSln6dGzA.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Our Evanston\, Illinois Wellness and Meditation Center offers 
 a free group guided meditation for peace\, mindfulness\, and relaxation. W
 elcoming you the first Friday of each month 6:30pm – 7:30pm.  We have b
 een providing this free community event in the Northshore area for over 28
  years.  We begin with gentle breathing techniques followed by short Nati
 ve American drumming into the guided meditation. \n\nMSI Wellness Center 2
 144 Ashland Ave Suite \\#1 Evanston IL 60201 \n\n847-866-0505    msi-hea
 ling.com \n\nAbout Your Guide: \n\nBillie Topa Tate is a Native Author & M
 escalero Apache Teacher – founder of MSI Wellness Center and from the Me
 scalero Apache Tradition dedicated to “Creating a Sacred Space One Perso
 n a Time” through the indigenous native teachings. She is the author of 
 several meditation recordings and books\, including her new book Spirit Gu
 ide Invocation – Seeking Help from Sacred Helpers.
LOCATION:MSI Wellness Center
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/free-community-meditation-first-fridays
 -630pm/2026-05-01/
