ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/rCn2RqqJ-UGUfWAzZoqLtg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for an unforgettable afternoon of games\, creativity
 \, and family-friendly excitement at Ignite Arcade's Family Fun Fest! Join
  us on Saturday\, May 2\, 2026 from 12:00 PM – 5:00 PM for a lively cele
 bration designed for kids\, parents\, and gamers of all ages. Whether your
  family loves crafts\, characters\, or classic arcade fun\, there will be 
 something for everyone to enjoy. Special Highlights • Meet and take phot
 os with Pikachu\, Princess Peach\, and other fun costumed characters • C
 reate your own Princess Peach crown or decorate a superhero cape • Get a
  custom design from our airbrush tattoo artist • Enjoy balloon creations
 \, arts & crafts stations\, and more interactive activities for kidsAnd of
  course\, don't miss the arcade! Ignite Arcade is proud to be the biggest 
 arcade on the North Shore\, featuring 100\\+ arcade cabinets\, fresh games
 \, and exciting prizes waiting to be won. Bring your friends\, bring the g
 randparents\, and come spend an afternoon filled with laughter\, creativit
 y\, and nonstop fun.
LOCATION:Ignite Arcade
URL:https://www.visitchicagonorthshore.com/events/family-fun-fest-at-ignit
 e-arcade-2026-05-02
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
