BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Infinite Wrench
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T200000
UID:2603190acxZKEbPUySe2dtRrgbZA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/qSPEIcEvrkKxVc_tWvebmg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Don’t miss the longest running late-night show in Chicago! \
 n\nAt The Infinite Wrench you’ll see 30 original plays in 60 minutes wri
 tten and performed by The Neo-Futurist Ensemble. Each play offers somethin
 g different\, be it funny\, profound\, elegant\, disgusting\, topical\, ir
 reverent\, terrifying\, or a song\; all are truthful and tackle the here-a
 nd-now. \n\nWith new plays every week. The Infinite Wrench is The Neo-Fut
 urists’ ongoing and ever-changing attempt to shift the conventions of li
 ve performance and speak to those unreached or unmoved by traditional thea
 ter.
LOCATION:The Neo-Futurist Theater
URL:https://www.choosechicago.com/event/the-infinite-wrench/2026-05-02/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SPINOFF
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T190000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T210000
UID:260318LPgyxPKNp0Kisbe5-mvr7A
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/IkS4GEmr9kqB0RBq4JAebg.large.png
DESCRIPTION:Two years ago\, Alé left the city to move back into their chi
 ldhood home to caretake for their mother. Far from friends\, their plans i
 n the wind\, Alé turned to the familiar world of TV sitcoms for comfort. 
 That’s when Alé discovered Frasier.\n\nNow\, it’s time for Alé ’s
  SPINOFF. Using the script of Frasier as a roadmap\, the cast of performer
 s will explore this time in Alé’s life\, deconstructing the sitcom form
  through the Neo-Futurist lens. Who are we to our parents\, who are they t
 o us\, what’s changed in the years apart?\n\nThe parent and the child. T
 he character and the person. Living under the same roof again\, will they 
 get picked up for syndication? Or canceled before they can tell the whole 
 story?
LOCATION:The Neo-Futurist Theater
URL:https://www.choosechicago.com/event/spinoff/2026-05-02/
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
