DESCRIPTION:Thirsty Thursday is an event hosted by Sketchbook Brewing Comp
 any \\(4901 Main Street\, Skokie\, IL\\) in conjunction with the Evanston 
 Homebrew Club. This gathering is meant to bring together homebrewers\, pot
 ential homebrewers and craft beer ethusiasts to sample and evaluate homebr
 ewed beers. Two of the founding principles of the Evanston HomebrewClub is
  to promote the craft of homebrewing and share our appreciation of craft b
 eers. This event gives us an opportunity to showcase your latest batch\, g
 et some constructive feedback\, and try out other brews as well. If you&\\
 #39\;re a homebrewer\, feel free to bring a couple of samples to share wit
 h your friends. If you&\\#39\;re not homebrewing \\(yet\\)\, feel free to 
 stop on by\, enjoy a pint or two of Sketchbook&\\#39\;s latest creations\,
  and make a friend or three.
