BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:VentureCat 2026 Public Showcase
DTSTART;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260527T180000
DTEND;TZID=CDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260527T193000
UID:2603267imQ_-trfE64cniLL5KqPQ
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/g-8mH_4iu0WNxxaXjmiM6Q.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:VentureCat is Northwestern’s annual student startup competi
 tion and celebrates the University’s most promising student founders.\n\
 nThe program culminates in a pitch competition in which a prize pool of $1
 75K\\+ in non-dilutive prize money is distributed to student ventures.\n\n
 Join us on Wednesday\, May 27 at 6 PM CT for the Public Showcase where we
  will feature the six finalist teams and their pitches. You will get the 
 chance to vote to award our audience favorite prize and we will announce o
 ur finals prize winners–including the grand prize of $100\,000.\n\nOur s
 emifinalist teams will span five tracks - Business Products & Services\; C
 onsumer Products & Services\; Energy & Sustainability\; Life Sciences & Me
 dical Innovation\; and Social Impact.\n\nThe VentureCat Public Showcase is
  free and open to the public. If you would like to contribute to this im
 portant program\, your gift will support VentureCat resources and awards f
 or future participants. Join us in supporting tomorrow's leaders driving f
 orward groundbreaking solutions and fostering a culture of innovation at N
 orthwestern.
LOCATION:Northwestern University
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#!/show?location=Evanston,+IL&distance=
 5#/details/venturecat-2026-public-showcase/18403515/2026-05-27T18
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Evanston
END:VEVENT
